{"tid":52380,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"去完日本旅行返黎，發現男朋友聖誕節同班豬朋狗友去澳門","createTime":"2016-12-24T04:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-11T08:06:10.000Z","uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"270f4b6e895d5e05de4d056093f0a956316a21b6","tid":52380,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:32:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n前排d yen 咁平，咁小妹就同班姊妹去左日本旅行順便血拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁小妹就諗住平安夜返黎同男朋友過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知一返到黎<br />\n條仆街夠膽死同我講約左班frd 過大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁嗰班frd 我一直刀唔鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得佢教壞我男朋友<br />\n之後鬧過幾次架都係為左班豬朋狗友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我返到黎知道男朋友過澳門<br />\n我真係勁嬲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇搞錯呀要我自己一個過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋好驚條友出軌<br />\n好彩九龍公園有暖水池<br />\n可以同班姊妹呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a1a9ace41730efa8fa254ae82d9725da78247e","tid":52380,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:35:31.000Z","msg":"男人去叫雞啫 又唔係做鴨"},{"pid":"016a607122fde7f3f1b81084c91b821e29946f3e","tid":52380,"uid":44242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的<br />\n前排d yen 咁平，咁小妹就同班姊妹去左日本旅行順便血拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁小妹就諗住平安夜返黎同男朋友過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知一返到黎<br />\n條仆街夠膽死同我講約左班frd 過大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁嗰班frd 我一直<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都</span></span>唔鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得佢教壞我男朋友<br />\n之後鬧過幾次架都係為左班豬朋狗友<img src=